parameters:
\N<Zuuteruka>Heh, no need to worry about that. You're going to take it
off again soon anyway.
\N<Zuuteruka>Oops. Good timing, just as you're finishing up over there.

\N<Ryuda Soldier>Yeah, today's that special day, right? I'm not yet satisfied
with this woman, but unfortunately, we can't monopolize
these two just for ourselves.

\N<Seno>W-what are you talking about...? What have you been saying
since earlier...?

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe, tonight is the big unveiling ceremony, I guess? You
two will be participating in that from now on.

\N<Princess Consort Suia>An unveiling... ceremony? What on earth do you intend to
make us do in these outfits...!?

\N<Seno>Exactly! We're tired from dealing with you clowns! What more
do you want us to do!? Just let us rest already!

\N<Zuuteruka>Is that so? Well, I won't stop you if you really want to
rest, but...

\N<Seno>Tch...! Your insinuating way of speaking is making me
sick...!

\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... Well then, now that we've settled that, let's have
you come along.
